      "span_text": "The effects of plasma protein on HS and CS are shown in Fig. 1, A and B. Similar to our laboratory's previous study  , the initial coverage of HS and CS on RFPECs were 83.3 Ϯ 6.2 and 86.6 Ϯ 2.7%, respectively, in the presence of p-DMEM for 2 h."
